        Is flag of page enable.

        flag - FLAG_TELEPHONE FLAG_SMS FLAG_QQ FLAG_WECHAT FLAG_FACEBOOK FLAG_TWITTER FLAG_LINKEDIN FLAG_INSTAGRAM FLAG_PINTEREST FLAG_WHATSAPP FLAG_LINE FLAG_FACEBOOK_MESSENGER FLAG_OTHERS_APP FLAG_PHONE_WARING FLAG_DEVICE_WARING FLAG_KAKAO FLAG_SKYPE
